            <h1>MES Tent</h1>
            <hr class="hr-primary">
            <p>MES Clubs, Teams and Groups can book the MES Tent for a variety of events. The Tent is 10′ by 15′, features a rainproof customized canopy and comes in a mobile transportation bag.</p>
            <h5><strong>Booking Instructions</strong></h5>
            <p>If you would like to book the MES Tent, you may email the AVP Services & Productions at avp.services@macengsociety.ca to check for availability before printing out the contract, which can be found below. Please note that upon booking the tent a $150 deposit in the form of cash or cheque must be given to the VP Finance. You must also be an MES Group, Team or Department Club as stated in the Policy Manual.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

