            <h5><strong>Booking Instructions</strong></h5>
            <p>If you would like to book the MES Trailer, you may email the Trailer Maintenance Coordinator at trailer@macengsociety.ca to check for availability before printing out the contract, which can be found below. Please note that in order to book the Trailer you must be an MES Group or Team.</p>
        </div>
